These are basically settings for what is said when your character enter or
leaves an area. To set find out how to set them look at 'help setmove'.
Your name will be added before all of these, so don't include it in the
setmove function, the exeption to this is mdest, which puts your name last and
the item first. Try to keep the message short (for disk space reasons).
the command  review  will let you see your current settings.
